WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.404 --> 00:00:15.404
 We make poppy seed. 

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:18.000
 Ingredients: 

00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:20.940
 8 dirty croissants, 

00:00:21.400 --> 00:00:23.480
 10 dkg minced poppy seed 

00:00:23.480 --> 00:00:25.187
 10 dkg crystal sugar 

00:00:25.187 --> 00:00:27.040
 1 lemon, 

00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:29.400
 2 bags of vanilla sugar 

00:00:30.920 --> 00:00:32.920
 5 dl of milk 

00:00:33.382 --> 00:00:35.382
 5 dkg butter. 

00:00:36.134 --> 00:00:41.974
 The milk is poured into a dish. 

00:00:45.979 --> 00:00:50.139
 Add the vanilla sugar. 

00:00:50.320 --> 00:00:52.320
 Bring to the boil. 

00:00:56.894 --> 00:01:05.134
 We cut out the spices. 

00:01:06.776 --> 00:01:10.116
 The poppy is poured into a bowl. 

00:01:12.820 --> 00:01:17.980
 Slice the lemon peel. 

00:01:26.193 --> 00:01:30.813
 Add half the crystal sugar. 

00:01:31.440 --> 00:01:33.840
 Mix. 

00:01:34.040 --> 00:01:37.260
 The other half of sugar, 

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:41.380
 added to the milk. 

00:01:41.720 --> 00:01:45.640
 Mixed. 

00:01:47.460 --> 00:01:54.800
 We make a glass bowl. 

00:01:59.116 --> 00:02:02.876
 We put the spatula in a row. 

00:02:02.876 --> 00:02:05.336
 We woke up, 

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:10.040
 with sugar milk. 

00:02:10.040 --> 00:02:15.100
 Sprinkle with poppy seeds. 

00:02:16.440 --> 00:02:20.280
 Let's put another layer of curds on milk. 

00:02:20.900 --> 00:02:24.394
 Then again poppy. 

00:02:25.340 --> 00:02:30.280
 We pack it until the materials are consumed. 

00:02:41.957 --> 00:02:47.477
 Dip the top with milk. 

00:02:56.580 --> 00:03:00.260
 then sprinkled with poppy seeds. 

00:03:03.440 --> 00:03:06.700
 In preheated oven 

00:03:07.080 --> 00:03:10.580
 20 minutes on a small flame 

00:03:10.580 --> 00:03:11.080
 bake in red. 

00:03:15.800 --> 00:03:20.000
 We are located. 

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:48.100
 Enjoy your meal. 

